package tegmentum:python-kdf-cap@0.1.0;

/// Companion WIT for CPython's `_kdf_cap` static extension. The C
/// extension imports the capabilities listed below; composectl/wac wires
/// them to their multiplexer / cap-component wasm at compose time.

// NOTE: this world depends on capability WIT files under wit/deps/.
// You must vendor each capability's .wit (and its transitive deps)
// before `wit-bindgen c --world kdf-cap-import --out-dir gen wit/` will succeed.
// The README walks through this.

world kdf-cap-import {
    import tegmentum:password-hash-multiplexer/password-dispatcher@0.1.0;
}
